name: AstronomyPictureoftheDay
0:
”alexa ask astro pic for the picture”
”alexa ask astro pic what is the picture of the day”
”alexa tell astro pic to give me the picture of the day”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: astro pic
des: The Astronomy Picture of the Day will send you the daily astronomy picture with the title and a brief description. The picture will be delivered directly to your Alex app for your viewing please. It is very easy to get started, simply ask "astro pic" for the picture or ask "astro pic", what is the picture of the day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
